window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Zane's become a regional powerhouse. Now he’ll see how he stacks up against the best in the world.</b></p> <p>He’s off to an elite summit where he’ll face off against the strongest fighters the world has to offer. A wealth of resources is up for grabs—if you’ve got the strength to seize them. It’ll push Zane to his very limits.</p> <p>Meanwhile Mike Masters, the mafia ruler of Southern California, has learned Zane’s been killing off his minions—and he’s coming for vengeance. And Zane's estranged brother Jason, king of the East Coast, has a bone to pick with him too.</p> <p><b>To be the best, you’ve got to beat the best. And Zane will rise to the challenge.</b></p>"; 
